	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001141_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'--> 
<!--Hand 01 21 top left--><!--Hand 02 67464 top right--><!--Hand 03 <p>Livingstone</p><p>b: 1817</p><p>d: 1873</p> top left-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>50 Albemarle <choice><abbr>St</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">28<hi rend="sup">th</hi><choice><abbr>Nov<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>November</expan></choice></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Taylor</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Our plans came 
<lb/>all to nothing and 
<lb/>I was partly to 
<lb/>blame for not 
<lb/>writing you at once 
<lb/>and more for 
<lb/>not enlightening 
<lb/>my better half too 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001141_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'--> 
<lb/>I was on the point 
<lb/>of starting for 
<lb/>Lisbon yesterday 
<lb/>&amp; had all packed up 
<lb/>for Southampton 
<lb/>but on going to 
<lb/>our minister to 
<lb/>Portugal before 
<lb/>starting he informed 
<lb/>me that such 
<lb/>was the paralysis 
<lb/>produced by the 
<lb/><term type="medical">epidemic</term> that no 
<lb/>business could be 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001141_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'--> 
<lb/>transacted at Lisbon 
<lb/>I have therefore to 
<lb/>wait another 
<w>fort-<lb break="no"/>night</w><!--two hyphens--> before going 
<lb/>I made a desperate 
<lb/>effort to explain 
<lb/>&amp; apologize in person 
<lb/>but blundered in 
<lb/>on Saturday when 
<lb/>you were of course 
<lb/>not there. I shall 
<lb/>come the first time 
<lb/>I can manage it 
<lb/>I have to draw up 
<lb/>my requisition 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001141_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'--> 
<lb/>and shew it here 
<lb/>on Monday. I 
<lb/>may go to Cambridge 
<lb/>as they want me 
<lb/>much and it is 
<lb/>a precious opportunity 
<lb/>Did not see <persName><choice><sic>Lord Skeleme
<lb/>rsdale</sic><corr>Skelmersdale</corr></choice></persName>. He did not 
<lb/>come. My kindest 
<lb/><del type="strikethrough">love</del> salutations to<persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rs</hi></hi> T.</persName> &amp; <persName>aunt <unclear cert="medium">Gretty</unclear></persName>
<lb/>and all. May all 
<lb/>grace abound towards 
<lb/>you all from our 
<lb/>common Lord</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
			
